java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, org.jdom2.NamespaceAware, org.jdom2.Parent, Fixable, Identifiable
public class SParam
extends AStruct

The concrete implementation of complex parameter meta definitions, being an extended wrapper to the SParam entry in DesignSpace.xsl. SParams can either be of user customizable type, such as String, without specific user choices, or with a set of choices that can be selected as alternatives for an instance of a design space.

Felix Dobslaw
